These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, bellflower
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Flower   | rose | bellflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Flower   | dahlia | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Cigar   | game | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, mystery
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | crime |

